        @Nonnull
public eu.bitwalker.useragentutils.Version getBrowserVersion()
        Delegate method Detects the detailed version information of the browser. Depends on the userAgent to be available. Use it only after using UserAgent(String) or UserAgent.parseUserAgent(String). Returns UserAgent.UNKNOWN_VERSION if it can not detect the version information.
